Here are the very important things for azure powershell

1. install azurepowershell 


How to connect to azure from powershell?

    1. Certificate method
      this method is essentially importing the certificate file 
      import -azurepublicationsettingfile PathToThe CertificateFile
   2. account method
      this method uses the subscription name to connect azure
      add-azureaccount 
      

Connection mode
  1. azure service management
  2. azure resource manager
  
